Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:28.78,scr,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs14\bord3\shad0\c&HE6B00C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(366.2,83.6)}青\N空\N{\c&H539718&}搞\N笑\N{\c&H956BE3&}大\N會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,今次也會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,之前年末的···
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事以後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,（應聘人必看！ 就職活動必勝法）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.04,0:22:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,再讓我嚐嚐炸雞塊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我會像媽媽說的那樣   無論用甚麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也一定要實現夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,柿花   差不多該休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.72,0:23:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.32,0:23:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,您要去哪裏
